e to support her two sons david learned bookkeeping from his mother who managed a cleaning crew at night growing up with no father and living through very difficult times david developed a desire to become something more not only for himself but for his family work history in  david started at georgetown college a small liberal arts college in georgetown ky david majored in marketing and finance he also minored in communications with a focus on theatre he graduated in may of  with a bachelor of science degree in june of  david started his first job at citizens fidelity bank in louisville kentucky david’s work started as a bank manager in retail banking then quickly moved into commercial lending where he made small to middle market loans to commercial businesses in september of  david was offered a position with ameritrust bank in cincinnati ohio as the manager of a new banking office concept that combined retail and commercial banking and personal investments into a single office there he managed several loan officers and stock brokers in september  david joined seasongood  mayer as an investment banking associate at seasongood david was classically trained in state state agency county city school district special district tid’s cfa’s sid’s and cog finance by the time he left seasongood in  david had managed more than  financings totaling in excess of  billion david earned his series  and series  david joined robert w baird and co in  as a managing director david undertook an initiative to build a business platform that would place robert w baird among the most recognized public finance firms in the state of ohio during his time at baird the company’s market share grew substantially between  and  baird ended among the top five investment banks in ohio having accomplished his goals david left baird in january  on a personal note many know david as their banker advisor or coworker but noahl amanda and tanner know him as “dad” when his children were asked how do you see him their replies were “strong  dedicated good hearted and loving person” his wife and best friend trish describes him as one of the most giving sensitive and dedicated persons that she has ever met last but not least david is also known as granpa kodi raine was born on david and trish’s anniversary and will be turning  in may of  as david builds rockmill financial he and trish are also focused on family time with the children and grandchild out on their  acres near the original rockmill farm in lancaster ohio ohio government financial advisors  rockmill financial consulting navigationwho we are     about rockmill     david j conleyservices     public finance     economic development     asset management     financial communications     budget  forecasting     research  analysiscontactresources     ballot millage calculator     downloadspartners independent partnership skilled reliable thorough effective thoughtful passionate valued resourceful unprecedented unbiased solutions as an independent municipal advisor and financial consultant we exist to provide you guidance understanding confidence and control regarding your financial matters whatever they may be you have questions… we have the answers the experts at rockmill financial specialize in solving today’s most complex and challenging financial issues faced by all governments for state state agencies counties schools cities and port authorities we make what seems impossible possible our team uses high level data driven techniques to provide truly innovative and effective solutions you want to be certain… we give you confidence the confidence to know that your financing contains the best terms and conditions possible when you work with our team we work to review every possible aspect and opportunity available to you for your borrowing needs you never have to wonder if you are getting a good deal we assure it as a registered municipal advisor your success is our business public finance reliable guidance for exce